(4, 31, 'Dentistry', '<h2>DENTAL CENTRE</h2><p><br></p><p>A comprehensive Dental Centre became operational at United Hospital on 29th April 2012. The Dental Centre has been set up with the aim to provide an international standard dental treatment facility to satisfy and meet the demands of our community.</p><p>Our dentists Dr Md. Nazrul Islam and Dr Lutfun Nahar both completed their Masters from National University of Singapore and have a 5-years working experience in Singapore.</p>', '<h2>OUR SERVICES INCLUDE</h2><p><br></p><ul><li>Scaling and polishing</li><li>Tooth color restoration</li><li>Dental implants</li><li>Implant over denture</li><li>Complete denture</li><li>Full mouth rehabilitation</li><li>Cosmetic filling</li><li>Dental crown and bridge</li><li>Teeth whitening</li><li>Root canal</li><li>Smile makeover</li><li>Dental CT Scan</li><li>Dental clearance for cancer patients</li></ul>', '<h2>DENTAL IMPLANT-YOUR 2ND PERMANENT TOOTH</h2><p><br></p><p>Missing or lost teeth is nothing to laugh about as it can change your smile forever. When a tooth is lost, its opposite tooth becomes inactive as it requires two opposite teeth to bite. So loosing teeth doesn’t only change your smile but it also compromises your functionality as well. But now we can bring back missing teeth with dental implants.</p><p>Dental Implants are small titanium screws that allow bone to grow in and around it. They are inserted in the jaw bone to mimic the teeth root and in due time an artificial tooth is attached with it to replace the missing tooth. Then the treatment is finished and the new tooth on implant looks and works just like a natural tooth. For patients who have no teeth, with the help of implants, we can restore full functional set of teeth for them. The functionality and appearance of implant supported tooth is as good as any natural tooth. So if you have any missing tooth, dental implants can be your 2nd permanent tooth.</p>', '<p><br></p>', '<p><br></p>', '202302281004dental.png', 1, 0, '2022-09-14 02:29:21', '2023-02-28 17:04:33'),
