(60, 132, 'Urology', '<h2>UROLOGY</h2>\n\n<p>Urology can be broadly defined as the specialty that manages patients with diseases of the male and female urinary tract, and of the male reproductive organs. It covers a wide range of common conditions including urinary tract infections, urinary tract stones, problems with bladder emptying, urinary incontinence and erectile dysfunction. Urologists also treat patients with kidney, bladder, prostate, penile and testicular cancer. The last of these typically affects younger men than most cancers; prostate cancer, on the other hand, is most often seen in older patients.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Best Urologists in Dhaka</strong></p>\n\n<p>The Department of Urology of United Hospital Limited, Dhaka is dedicated to provide state-of-the-art medical and surgical care with the best Urologists in the country for all specialties of male and female urology (both adult and pediatric).</p>\n\n<p>CONSULTATION &amp; APPOINTMENT</p>\n\n<p>Our Urologists are considered among the best in Dhaka. The department provides consultation services through highly qualified and experienced Urology Consultant.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Urology conditions treated here:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Kidney Stone</li>\n	<li>Urinary Tract Infection</li>\n	<li>Prostatitis</li>\n	<li>Polycystic Kidney Disease</li>\n	<li>Prostate Enlargement</li>\n	<li>Urinary Incontinence</li>\n	<li>Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia</li>\n	<li>Prostate Cancer</li>\n	<li>Erectile Dysfunction</li>\n	<li>Male Infertility</li>\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '2022-09-19 10:59:40', '2022-10-06 16:50:24'),
