(117, NULL, 'Anesthesiology', '<h2>ANESTHESIOLOGY</h2><p>The anesthesiologists on staff at United Hospital provide anesthesia services for inpatient and outpatient surgery as well as for non-surgical diagnostic and therapeutic procedures. Other services include obstetric pain relief, and treatment of acute and chronic pain. Anesthesia service is available around the clock, seven days a week.&nbsp;Our anesthesiologists use the latest technology and proven techniques to maximize your comfort and safety—before, during, and after your procedure. They are exceptionally dedicated to the highest standards of their specialty.</p>', '<h2>FACILITIES</h2><p>Your anesthesiologist will fully explain your anesthesia options and outline the pros and cons of each approach.He or she will work with your surgeon to develop a individualized pre-op to post-op plan to:</p><ul><li>Anticipate any medical problems that could arise during surgery</li><li>Keep you pain-free through your surgery</li><li>Relieve anxiety</li><li>Control your body\'s reaction to stress</li><li>Minimize side effects</li><li>Make your recovery easier</li></ul><p>In addition to administering anesthetic during your procedure, your anesthesiologist will monitor your vital body functions, such as breathing, blood oxygen saturation, blood pressure, heart rate, and kidney functions. After surgery your anesthesiologist will closely monitor you for any problems related to your anesthetic and order pain medication as your condition allows.</p>', '<p><br></p>', '<p><br></p>', '<p><br></p>', '202302281010anesthology.png', 0, 1, '2023-02-26 16:38:14', '2023-03-01 18:39:48'),
(118, NULL, 'Ophthalmology (Eye Care)', '<h2>OPHTHALMOLOGY</h2><p><br></p><p>The Department of Ophthalmology of United Hospital provides both basic and specialized eye care services for patients. Our trained and experienced Consultant provides specialized treatment for a wide variety of eye problems.</p><p>Specialized equipment such as the argon laser for treatment of diabetic eye diseases, and computerized visual field analysers for assessment of glaucoma, are available. Our Consultant, trained in optometry, helps in the prescription of glasses for both adults and children. All surgeries are conducted at state-of-the-art operation theatres of the hospital, and over 90% of the surgeries do not require hospital admission. The theatre is equipped with a phaco-emulsification machine for small incision cataract surgery.</p>', '<h2>CONSULTATION &amp; APPOINTMENTS</h2><p><br></p><p>The department provides consultation services in level-4 through highly qualified and experienced Consultant, who carefully evaluates each patient. After diagnosing the patient’s condition, our Consultant discusses available treatment options and recommends the most effective treatment.</p>', '<h2>SERVICES AVAILABLE IN EYE CARE CENTRE :</h2><p><br></p><ul><li>Computerized Eye Test</li><li>Slit Lamp Eye Test</li><li>Tonometry</li><li>Glaucoma Screening</li><li>Contact Lens</li><li>Eyelid Surgery</li><li>Congenital Autograft</li><li>Cornea Transplantation</li><li>Squint Surgery</li><li>Glaucoma Surgery</li><li>DCR Surgery</li><li>Phaco Surgery</li></ul><p><br></p>', NULL, NULL, '202302270532ophthalmology.png', 1, 0, '2023-02-27 12:32:10', '2023-02-27 12:32:10'),
(119, NULL, 'Gastroenterology & Hepatology', '<h2>GASTRO LIVER CENTRE</h2><p><br></p><p>Department of Gastroenterology &amp; Hepatology is devoted to the clinical care of patients with gastrointestinal and liver disorders. The department is home to excellent patient care, and our specialists employ the most advanced diagnostic and therapeutic endoscopy services to ensure the best outcomes for each patient.</p>', '<h2>SERVICES :</h2><p><br></p><ul><li>Endoscopy upper&nbsp;GI Tract</li><li>Colonoscopy</li><li>Enteroscopy</li><li>ERCP</li><li>Polypectomy</li><li>Capsule Endoscopy</li></ul><p><br></p>', '<h2>CONSULTATION &amp; APPOINTMENTS :</h2><p><br></p><p>The Department provides consultation services in 1st &amp; 2nd Floor 3 (OPD 2 &amp; 3) through highly qualified and experienced Gastroenterology &amp; Hepatology Consultants.</p>', NULL, NULL, '202302270548gastroenterology (1).png', 1, 0, '2023-02-27 12:48:16', '2023-02-27 12:48:16'),
