(139, NULL, 'Neurosurgery', '<h2>NEUROSURGERY</h2><p><br></p><p>United Hospital has set up advanced Neurosurgery facilities in Bangladesh, through highly trained neurosurgeons and neurologists and the most modern equipments. As a result, United Hospital has established itself as the only hospital to provide comprehensive Neurosurgery facilities under one roof coupled with Neurology support</p><ul><li>Modern management of Stroke, Brain Haemorrhage, Brain Tumor and Paralysis</li><li>All surgeries of Brain &amp; Spinal Cord like brain tumour, trauma, disc prolapse and spinal cord compression including Microscopic Brain &amp; Spine Surgery, Minimally Invasive Spine Surgery, Endoscopic Neurosurgery</li><li>Dedicated state-of-the-art modern Neuro Operation Theater</li><li>Neuro-diagnostic facilities:</li><li>- 4&nbsp;500 slice CT Scan and non-invasive CT Angiogram</li><li>- 4&nbsp;1.5 Tesla HD MRI</li><li>- 4&nbsp;EEG, NCV and EMG</li><li>- 4&nbsp;Carotid Doppler</li><li>Comprehensive Neuro-rehabilitation services by experienced and well-trained physiotherapist</li></ul><p><br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '202302281329neurosurgery.png', 1, 0, '2023-02-28 20:29:17', '2023-02-28 20:29:17');
