(140, NULL, 'Vascular Surgery', '<h2>VASCULAR CENTER</h2><p><br></p><p>Healthy blood vessels are essential for a healthy body.</p><p>United Vascular Center (UVC) provides comprehensive patient care for the diagnosis, management and treatment of vascular diseases (diseases of blood vessels) and thrombotic (blood-clotting) disorders, as well as care of complex vascular wounds.</p><p>Our multidisciplinary team includes world renowned vascular and endovascular surgeons, nurses, vascular radiologists, pharmacists, physiotherapists and dieticians to coordinate your care and provide personalized consultations and follow-up.</p><p><br></p><h2><strong><u>DISEASES &amp; CONDITIONS WE TREAT</u></strong></h2><p><br></p><p><strong>A. Arterial Conditions</strong></p><p>- Abdominal Aortic Aneurysm (AAA)</p><p>- Aortic Dissection</p><p>- Carotid Artery Disease</p><p>- Peripheral Vascular Disease (PVD) of all kinds</p><p>- Thoracic Aortic Aneurysm (TAA)</p><p>- Arterial Gangrene</p><p>- Arterial Embolism</p><p>- Arterial Trauma</p><p><strong>B. Venous conditions</strong></p><p>- Varicose veins</p><p>- Chronic venous insufficiency</p><p>- Venous malformations</p><p>- Venous Ulcer</p><p>- Spider veins</p><p>- Deep vein thrombosis and IVC Filter insertion</p><p><strong>C. Lymphatic condition</strong></p><p>- Lymphoedema</p><p>- Elephanthiasis</p><p><strong>D. Congenital Vascular Malformations</strong></p><p><strong>E. Diabetic Foot and Gangrene</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://www.uhlbd.com/administrator/uploads/images/Untitled%281%29.jpg\"></p><p><strong>F. Vascular Access for dialysis</strong></p><p>- Full Range of vascular access surgery including AV grafts.</p><p>- CAPD catheter insertion.</p><p>- Portacath insertion.</p><h2><strong><u>VASCULAR CENTER LOCATED AT:</u></strong></h2><p>OPD-1. Room No: 8004</p><p>United Hospital Ltd.</p><p>Plot 15, Road 71, Gulshan, Dhaka-1212</p><h2><strong><u>APPOINTMENTS:</u></strong></h2><p>To schedule an appointment, call 10666/ 02 22 22 62 466.</p><p>5 p.m. to 7 p.m. (except Friday)</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '202302281333vascular-surgery.png', 1, 0, '2023-02-28 20:33:19', '2023-02-28 20:33:19'),
