(143, NULL, 'Interventional Cardiology', '<h2>CARDIOLOGY</h2><p>ABOUT THE DEPARTMENT</p><p><strong>The Best Cardiologist in Dhaka, Bangladesh</strong></p><p>United Hospital has the best cardiologists in Dhaka, Bangladesh providing specialized inpatient and outpatient heart care and long term management of the conditions. We offer the latest techniques and cardiac care to patients of all ages. We treat patients with common heart problems such as angina to rare heart conditions.</p><p>With the help of State-of-the-heart-technology, equipment and monitoring devices, our cardiologists are providing excellent heart care to all the patients. Our department has the best cardiologists and heart specialists in Dhaka, who are highly specialized and has years of experience and expertise in cardiac care.</p><p>Our cardiologists provide 24 hour dedicated service and is the only hospital of Bangladesh where emergency angioplasty can be carried out round the clock. It is operated by a strong and dedicated team of 4 cardiologists – Consultants Dr. N. A. M. Momenuzzaman, Dr. Kaisar Nasrullah Khan, Dr. Fatema Begum Dr. Reyan Anis and Dr. A. M. Shafique. With the help of their extensive knowledge and supreme clinical practices, we are well efficient to treat the significant procedures, the best heart specialists in the heart of the Country, Dhaka. United Hospital is holding the pride of having the best cardiologist in Dhaka, Bangladesh.</p><p>The Cardiology division of United Cardiac Center has modern electro-medical equipments and appliances which include 3 catheterization laboratories including the most advanced Azurion Cathlab, Cardio Neuro iGS 520 Hybrid Cathlab and a 20 bed Coronary Care Unit (CCU) with specially managed CCU unit dedicated for COVID patients to carry out all necessary procedures related to diagnostic &amp; interventional cardiology.</p><p>In addition to this, we have a 15 bedded Cardiac High Dependency Unit (CHDU) and an 8 bedded Post Cath Section.</p><p><img src=\"https://www.uhlbd.com/administrator/uploads/images/Cardiac%20Advt-Final_Output%281%29.png\"></p><h2>CARDIAC INVESTIGATION CONDUCTED AT OUR HOSPITAL ARE:</h2><ul><li>ECG</li><li>ECHO (2D-M Mode/ Colour Doppler)</li><li>HOLTER ECG</li><li>TRANSESOPHAGEAL ECHO</li><li>DOBUTAMINE INDUCED ECHO</li><li>TEE</li><li>ETT</li><li>CAG (Coronary Angiogram)</li><li>USG</li><li>CT Angio</li><li>24 Hours Ambulatory BP</li><li>24 Hours Monitoring</li><li>X-Ray Chest P/A View</li><li>Lipid Profile</li></ul><h2>THE FOLLOWING PROCEDURES ARE DONE BY OUR CARDIOLOGY TEAM:</h2><ul><li>CAG&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: Coronary Angiography</li><li>PTCA&nbsp;: Percutaneous Transluminal Coronary Angioplasty / Stenting</li><li>PTMC&nbsp;: Percutaneous Transluminal Mitral Comissurectomy</li><li>TPMI&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: Temporary Pace Maker Installation</li><li>PPMI&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: Permanent Pace Maker Installation</li><li>CRT&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: Cardiac Resynchronization Device</li><li>ICD or AICD : Implantable Cardioverter-Defibrillator or Automated Implantable Cardioverter-Defibrillator C.Cath Coil Embolisation</li><li>ASD&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: Atrial Septal Defect V. Plasty</li><li>TAVI&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: Transcathether aortic valve implantation</li><li>PV&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: Pulmonary Valvoplasty</li><li>Pace Maker Implementation</li></ul><h2>AN OVERALL GLANCE AT OUR STATE-OF-THE-ART FACILITIES</h2><ul><li>3 Catheterization Laboratories (Cath Labs) including one state-of-the-art Azurion Cathlab and one Cardio Neuro iGS 520 Hybrid Cathlab</li><li>20 Bed Coronary Care Unit/CCU</li><li>15 Bed Cardiac High Dependency Unit/CHDU</li><li>3 Cardiac Operation Theatres</li><li>24 Bed Cardiac ICU and Step-down CICU</li></ul><h2>CONSULTATION &amp; APPOINTMENT</h2><p>Cardiology Department provides consultation services in (OPD - 4) at 1st Floor through highly qualified, experienced and one of the best Cardiologists in Dhaka, Bangladesh. Call 10666 or 02 22 22 62 466 Extension 8114 and 8115) for appointment with one of the best Cardiologists in Dhaka, Bangladesh.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '202302281407cardiology (2).png', 0, 1, '2023-02-28 21:07:12', '2023-02-28 21:07:22'),
