(49, NULL, 'Dr. Soumen Chakraborty\r\n', '', 'EID-15681', 'A-43898\r\n', 16, NULL, 1500, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '2022-10-03 05:08:21', '2022-10-03 10:43:44'),
(50, NULL, 'Dr. Md. Helal Uddin', 'MBBS, D-Card, MSC', 'EID-15769', 'A-27282\r\n', 16, '2022100409341576145046_2_Dr. Md. Helal Uddin.jpg', 1500, '<p>He passed MBBS in 1997 from M.A.G Osmani Medical College, Sylhet. He did his MSC in Cardiology from Canterbury Christ Church University, UK in 2011. He completed his D-Card from National Institute of Cardiovascular Disease (NICVD), Dhaka in 2002. He also had training in Non-invasive Cardiology from Escort Heart Institute, India. He worked in Square Hospital as Specialist from 2007 to 2010. Thereafter he joined in United Hospital as a Junior Consultant in Cardiology Department from 2012 till now.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '2022-10-03 05:08:21', '2022-10-04 16:34:51'),
(51, NULL, 'Dr. Mohammad Rafiur Rahman', 'MBBS, MS (CTS)', 'EID-15861', 'A38844\r\n', 15, '2022100409341639478377_2_1615697644_2_dr rafi.jpg', 1500, '<ul>\n	<li>Obtained MBBS degree from Mymensingh Medical College under University of Dhaka in 2003</li>\n	<li>Completed MS in Cardio-Thoracic Surgery (CTS) from National Heart Foundation Hospital &amp; Research Institute (NHFH&amp;RI) under Dhaka University in 2014</li>\n	<li>Worked in National Heart Foundation Hospital &amp; Research Institute (NHFH&amp;RI), Mirpur, Dhaka at Cardiac Surgery Department as Surgical Resident from 2005 to 2014</li>\n	<li>After completing post-graduation degree he served as Junior Consultant in the departments of Cardiac Surgery in Chottogram Metropolitan Hospital, Dr. Sirajul Islam Medical College Hospital and Bangladesh Specialized Hospital from 2014 to 2018</li>\n	<li>Joined United Hospital in 2018 and at present serving as Junior Consultant in the department of Cardiac Surgery</li>\n	<li>In the United Hospital Cardiac Surgery department, he is actively and successfully participating to his full capacity in Bypass Grafting Surgery (CABG), Aortic and Mitral Valve Surgeries (Replacement and Repair), Congenital Heart Surgeries like ASD, VSD and PDA repair surgeries on a regular basis</li>\n	<li>He has attended several workshops abroad (Italy, India) related to Advanced Cardiac Surgery such as Valve Repair Surgery, Aortic Surgery and Heart Transplant and Mechanical Circulatory support Devices Surgery</li>\n	<li>Very much interested in Total Arterial Bypass Grafting Surgery, Aortic Surgery, Valve Repair Surgery, Minimal Invasive Cardiac Surgery (MICS), Heart Transplant and Various Short &amp; Long term Mechanical Circulatory Assist Devices Surgery</li>\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '2022-10-03 05:08:21', '2022-10-04 16:34:12'),
(52, NULL, 'Dr. S.M. Sadlee', 'MBBS,MRCP (UK)', 'EID-16015', 'A53671\r\n', 79, '2022100409311647866034_2_Dr. S. M. Sadlee.jpg', 1500, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '2022-10-03 05:08:21', '2022-10-04 16:31:57'),
(53, NULL, 'Dr. Naima Siddiquee', 'MBBS, FCPS (Physical Medicine)', 'EID-16210', 'A-48195\r\n', 104, '2022100409311570362189_2_IMG_4552_edit.jpg', 1500, '<p>Dr. Naima Siddiquee passed MBBS in 2007 from Sir Salimullah Medical College under University of Dhaka. She has done her FCPS in PM&amp;R on 2014 from Bangladesh College of Physicians and Surgeons. She has had extensive hands-on training on PM&amp;R in DMCH &amp; BSMMU. She worked in various hospitals as physiatrist (PM&amp;R physician) and was in her own private practice before joining UHL.</p>\n\n<p>EDUCATION AND QUALIFICATIONS</p>\n\n<p>1. MBBS &ndash; Sir Salimullah Medical College, under University of Dhaka - 2007</p>\n\n<p>2. FCPS (Physical Medicine &amp; Rehabilitation)&ndash; Bangladesh College of Physicians and Surgeons &ndash; 2014</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '2022-10-03 05:08:21', '2022-10-04 16:31:36'),
(54, NULL, 'Dr. Md. Matiur Rahman', 'MBBS, MD(Card), FCPS', 'EID-16234', 'A-46186\r\n', 16, '2022100409301576146477_2_Dr. Md. Matiur Rahman.jpg', 1500, '<p>He passed MBBS in 2006 from Rangpur Medical College. He did his FCPS in Medicine from Bangladesh College of Physicians and Surgeons (BCPS) in 2015. He completed his MD in Cardiology from Dhaka Medical College in 2017. He worked in East West Medical College as Assistant Professor from 2017 to 2018. Before joining at United Hospital he worked in Ibn Sina Cardiac Centre as a Resident Consultant in 2018.</p>\n\n<table>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><strong>OPD TIMING: 06:00 PM To 09:00 PM,&nbsp;DAYS: SUNDAY,&nbsp;TUESDAY&nbsp;&amp; THURSDAY</strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>', NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '2022-10-03 05:08:21', '2022-10-04 16:30:07');
