(956, 'SQLSTATE[HY000]: General error: 1366 Incorrect integer value: \'Anesthesiology\' for column \'dept_id\' at row 1 (SQL: update `doctors` set `dept_id` = Anesthesiology, `doctor_desc` = <p>Dr. Ashia Ali did her graduation (MBBS) from Rangpur Medical College under University of Rajshahi in 1986. She did her Diploma in Anesthesia from University of Dhaka in 1998 and FCPS (Anesthesia) in 2003. She served in Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujib Medical University in the department of Cardiothoracic Anesthesia for long 11 years from 2003 to 2014. Thereafter she joined Apollo Hospitals Dhaka (now Evercare Hospital) as Consultant Anesthesia &amp; ICU and served there from 2014 till 2016. Before joining United Hospital, she served Asgar Ali Hospital as Consultant of Anesthesia &amp; Pain Medicine from end 2016 till mid-2020.</p><p>Dr Ashia is an expert in management of knee pain, back pain, shoulder pain, neck pain and post-operative long standing pain in addition to managing diabetes complications as in frozen shoulder, any cases of slip disc, severe myalgia and neuralgia. Managing cancer induced pain using Intrathecal pump to deliver morphine in spinal cord, is one of her special proficiency. She is a skilled practitioner of epidural injection, PRP (platelet rich plasma) therapy, ozone (O3) discectomy, dry needling, radio frequency ablation etc in minimizing different painful conditions.</p>, `doctor_edu` = null, `doctor_exp` = null, `doctors`.`updated_at` = 2023-02-28 04:44:16 where `id` = 62)', '712', '/home/k0zqcqav51nm/public_html/unitedhospitalapi/vendor/laravel/framework/src/Illuminate/Database/Connection.php', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/110.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', 'Apache', 1, '1743047506', '1', '0', '2023-02-28 11:44:16', '2023-02-28 04:44:16'),
