(97, NULL, 'Dr. Md. Abdul Mabin', 'MBBS (DMC), DSS (Vienna), Fellow in Specialized Surgery (Plastic & Reconstructive)', 'HS00131\r\n', '6380\r\n', 106, '2022100408291612942730_2_Dr.-Md.-Abdul-Mabin1.jpg', 1500, '<p><br></p>', '<ul><li>Obtained MBBS in 1977 from Dhaka Medical College.</li><li>Completed Diploma in Specialized Surgery (Plastic and Reconstructive) in 1983 from University of Vienna Post Graduate School of Medicine, Vienna, Austria and Completed Fellow in Specialized Surgery (Plastic and Reconstructive) in 1983 from Department of Plastic and Reconstructive, 1st Surgical University Clinic, Vienna, Austria.</li><li>Member of American Medical Society of Vienna, Austria, American Society of Laser Medicine and Surgery, USA and also member of Life Member Society of Plastic Surgeons of Bangladesh &amp; The International society of Aesthetic Plastic Surgery, USA.</li><li>Worked in Dhaka Medical College Hospital as Assistant Surgeon, Kitwe Central and Hospital, Ministry of Health, Zambia as Senior Resident Medical Officer, Hlatikulu Government Hospital, Ministry of Health, Kingdom of Swaziland as Medical Officer and Ministry of Petrolium, Iran as Plastic Surgeon.</li><li>Worked as a Consultant Plastic Surgeon in The Specialized Hospital, Dhaka from 1999 to 2003.</li><li>Working with Eden Multi-Care Hospital as Consultant Plastic Surgeon since 2003.</li></ul><p><br></p>', 'null', 1, 0, '2022-10-03 05:08:21', '2022-11-14 17:14:11'),
