(138, NULL, 'Dr. Ashis Kumar Biswas', 'BDS, MCPS (Dental Surgery), FCPS (Orthodontic & Dentofacial Orthopaedics)', 'HS01899\r\n', '2581\r\n', 31, '2022100405581572689027_2_Dr Asish.jpg', 1500, '<p>Dr. Ashis Kumar graduated (BDS) from Chittagong Medical College in 2005; He did his&nbsp; MCPS in Dental Surgery from Bangladesh College of Physicians &amp; Surgeons (BCPS) in 2010 and completed FCPS in Orthodontic and Dentofacial Orthopaedics from&nbsp; Bangladesh College of Physicians &amp; Surgeons (BCPS)&nbsp; in 2012.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Dr. Ashis Kumar worked in Udayan Dental College, Rajshahi as Assistant Professor and Head, Department of Orthodontics from October 2012 to April 2013. Thereafter he joined&nbsp; as&nbsp; Assistant Professor in Department of Orthodontics&nbsp; of Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujib Medical University, Dhaka (BSMMU)&nbsp; in June 2013. He has more than 14 years clinical experience in Dental Surgery and Orthodontic. He is the member of Bangladesh Orthodontic Society.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '2022-10-03 05:08:21', '2022-10-04 12:58:45'),
(139, NULL, 'Prof. Dr. Md.Nurul Islam', 'MBBS, MRCP (UK), FRCP (Edin)', 'HS01902\r\n', '7705\r\n', 78, '2022100405511639478485_2_1574338102_2_IMG_5519_edit.jpg', 1500, '<ul><li>Obtained MBBS degree from Rajshahi Medical College under University of Rajshahi in 1978</li><li>Completed MRCP in Medicine in 1993 and obtained FRCP in Medicine in 2005 from Royal College of Physicians of Edinburgh (UK)</li><li>Received extensive training on different disciplines of Renal Transplantation from Jeddah Kidney Centre and King Fahad Hospital Madinah, Kingdom of Saudi Arabia</li><li>Served in different institutions of home and abroad like Rajshahi Medical College, Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujib Medical University (BSMMU), BIRDEM and Yanbu General Hospital, Madinah, under Ministry of Health, Kingdom of Saudi Arabia</li><li>Worked in BIRDEM as Associate Professor &amp; Head of the Department of Nephrology from 2001 to 2007 where he led 25 kidney transplantations</li><li>Thereafter joined in Bangladesh Medical College and Hospital and served as Professor of Nephrology from 2007 to 2008</li><li>Served in United Hospital as Consultant Nephrologist and Chief Transplant Coordinator from 2008 to 2017 leading 39 kidney transplantations</li><li>Worked in Asgar Ali Hospital Dhaka as Consultant in the Department of Nephrology from 2017 to 2018</li><li>Before re-joining United Hospital he was working in Impulse Hospital as Senior Consultant in the Department of Nephrology from 2018 to 2019</li></ul>', 'null', 'null', 1, 0, '2022-10-03 05:08:21', '2022-11-22 16:56:22'),
